1011
00:57:35,719 --> 00:57:38,620
- YOU'RE GONNA BE FINE.

1012
00:57:38,622 --> 00:57:40,889
WE'RE GONNA GET YOU
TO A HOSPITAL

1013
00:57:40,891 --> 00:57:42,257
ONE WAY OR ANOTHER.

1014
00:57:42,259 --> 00:57:43,592
I PROMISE.

1015
00:57:43,594 --> 00:57:46,862
[eerie ambient music]

1016
00:57:46,864 --> 00:57:55,170
♪

1017
00:57:56,206 --> 00:57:57,739
[gunshot]

1018
00:57:57,741 --> 00:57:59,875
- [groans]

1019
00:57:59,877 --> 00:58:01,844
[jibbers]

1020
00:58:12,222 --> 00:58:13,322
[roars]

1021
00:58:13,324 --> 00:58:15,324
[gunshot]

1022
00:58:17,026 --> 00:58:19,261
[pounding at door]

1023
00:58:19,263 --> 00:58:20,028
[gun cocks]

1024
00:58:20,030 --> 00:58:21,563
- GO AHEAD.
LET HIM IN.

1025
00:58:21,565 --> 00:58:22,731
OPEN THE DOOR.

1026
00:58:22,733 --> 00:58:24,933
[rapid knocking]

1027
00:58:24,935 --> 00:58:25,834
KELLY.

1028
00:58:25,836 --> 00:58:27,569
OPEN THE DOOR.
LET HIM IN.

1029
00:58:27,571 --> 00:58:29,905
I'M GONNA FUCKING BLOW
HIS HEAD OFF.

1030
00:58:29,907 --> 00:58:30,606
[knocking]

1031
00:58:30,608 --> 00:58:31,974
OPEN IT UP
AND GET BACK.

1032
00:58:31,976 --> 00:58:32,908
- [squeals fearfully]

1033
00:58:32,910 --> 00:58:35,177
- HEY, MATT!
WHAT THE FUCK?

1034
00:58:35,179 --> 00:58:37,145
ALMOST SHOT YOU!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

1035
00:58:37,147 --> 00:58:40,182
GET IN HERE!
WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH YOU?

1036
00:58:40,184 --> 00:58:42,851
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?
- HOLY FUCKING SHIT.

1037
00:58:42,853 --> 00:58:43,752
- ANDREW, GET A CHAIR.

1038
00:58:43,754 --> 00:58:46,054
- OH, MY GOD.
- SIT DOWN!

1039
00:58:46,056 --> 00:58:47,990
WHAT IS IT?

1040
00:58:47,992 --> 00:58:49,157
I ALMOST SHOT YOU!

1041
00:58:49,159 --> 00:58:49,858
- [cries]

1042
00:58:49,860 --> 00:58:51,793
- WHAT THE FUCK
IS WRONG WITH YOU?

1043
00:58:51,795 --> 00:58:54,096
HOLY SHIT.

1044
00:58:54,098 --> 00:58:55,898
GOD ALMIGHTY.

1045
00:58:55,900 --> 00:58:57,633
- I WAS AT THE STATION.

1046
00:58:57,635 --> 00:58:58,567
I'M THERE,

1047
00:58:58,569 --> 00:59:02,271
AND I'M FINISHING THE SHIFT;
I'M ALMOST DONE.

1048
00:59:02,273 --> 00:59:05,040
AND FUCKING
OUT OF NOWHERE,

1049
00:59:05,042 --> 00:59:07,643
OLD MAN TUMAN
FUCKING ATTACKS ME, MAN.

1050
00:59:07,645 --> 00:59:09,211
HE TAKES ME
TO THE FUCKING GROUND.

1051
00:59:09,213 --> 00:59:11,013
- YOU'RE GONNA FUCKING BLEED
TO DEATH.

1052
00:59:11,015 --> 00:59:14,182
GO GET SOMETHING
FOR THAT FUCKING THING.

1053
00:59:14,184 --> 00:59:16,084
- I'M DOWN--

1054
00:59:16,086 --> 00:59:17,052
YEAH, I'M DOWN, RIGHT?

1055
00:59:17,054 --> 00:59:20,956
I'VE BEEN WORKING FOR THE GUY,
FUCKING WHAT, 11 YEARS?

1056
00:59:20,958 --> 00:59:23,825
HE'S GOT TO BE, LIKE,
70 POUNDS.

1057
00:59:23,827 --> 00:59:26,128
[chuckles]

1058
00:59:26,130 --> 00:59:28,864
AND HE HIT ME--

1059
00:59:28,866 --> 00:59:32,801
HE HIM ME LIKE I AIN'T
NEVER BEEN HIT BEFORE, MAN,

1060
00:59:32,803 --> 00:59:33,835
EVER.

1061
00:59:33,837 --> 00:59:35,270
- THE FUCK HAPPEN
TO YOUR LEG?

1062
00:59:35,272 --> 00:59:37,339
- [cries painfully]

1063
00:59:37,341 --> 00:59:41,343
SO HE FALLS ON TOP OF ME,
AND HE'S--

1064
00:59:41,345 --> 00:59:43,145
AND HE'S TRYING TO BITE ME.

1065
00:59:43,147 --> 00:59:47,215
HE TRIED TO CHEW
MY FUCKING LEG OFF.

1066
00:59:47,217 --> 00:59:47,849
[groans]

1067
00:59:47,851 --> 00:59:55,157
SO I'M--I'M KICKING HIS FACE
AGAIN, AGAIN, AGAIN,

1068
00:59:55,159 --> 00:59:56,024
HARD, MAN.

1069
00:59:56,026 --> 00:59:56,825
I'M TELLING YOU.

1070
00:59:56,827 --> 00:59:59,127
I BROKE HIS FACE, LOUIS.
I DID.

1071
00:59:59,129 --> 01:00:00,696
NOTHING LEFT TO HIM

1072
01:00:00,698 --> 01:00:03,999
BEHIND THOSE EYES, MAN.

1073
01:00:04,001 --> 01:00:05,701
- FUCK.
- NOTHING.

1074
01:00:05,703 --> 01:00:09,371
- OKAY, THIS IS GONNA HURT.

1075
01:00:09,373 --> 01:00:11,640
- [screams]

1076
01:00:12,909 --> 01:00:14,710
[groaning]
I JUST FUCKING--

1077
01:00:14,712 --> 01:00:16,912
I JUST SPRAYED GAS
IN HIS EYES,

1078
01:00:16,914 --> 01:00:22,317
AND I CRAWLED IN THE TRUCK,
AND I RAN, MAN.

1079
01:00:22,319 --> 01:00:25,220
I RAN, LOUIS.

1080
01:00:32,028 --> 01:00:33,161
- CALM DOWN.

1081
01:00:33,163 --> 01:00:36,765
NEVER HAD A HABIT.

1082
01:00:37,967 --> 01:00:39,768
- ANDREW, TRY THE COPS AGAIN.

1083
01:00:39,770 --> 01:00:42,270
- [whimpering]

1084
01:00:42,272 --> 01:00:45,674
- ARE YOU EVEN LISTENING
TO ME?

1085
01:00:45,676 --> 01:00:48,710
THIS IS BIGGER THAN US.

1086
01:00:48,712 --> 01:00:52,280
- [panicked screaming]

1087
01:00:54,984 --> 01:00:58,420
[whimpering]

1088
01:01:04,260 --> 01:01:07,829
[panting]

1089
01:01:16,139 --> 01:01:18,106
- HEY, CAN YOU HELP ME?

1090
01:01:18,108 --> 01:01:20,008
PLEASE, THERE'S BEEN
AN ACCIDENT.

1091
01:01:20,010 --> 01:01:22,911
CAN YOU HELP ME, PLEASE?

1092
01:01:23,946 --> 01:01:27,449
I'LL DO ANYTHING
YOU WANT.

1093
01:01:29,218 --> 01:01:31,286
ANYTHING.

1094
01:01:32,422 --> 01:01:33,822
[gunshot]

1095
01:01:33,824 --> 01:01:35,457
[gasps]

1096
01:02:27,310 --> 01:02:29,144
- HI, GRANDMA.

1097
01:02:29,146 --> 01:02:32,247
UM, DRINK SOME WATER.

1098
01:02:36,052 --> 01:02:39,054
OKAY, OKAY.

1099
01:02:39,056 --> 01:02:39,821
THERE YOU GO.

1100
01:02:39,823 --> 01:02:42,457
YOU FEEL BETTER
A LITTLE BIT?

1101
01:02:42,459 --> 01:02:43,158
GOOD, GOOD.

1102
01:02:43,160 --> 01:02:44,960
LOOK, THIS IS A RAG.
IT'S COLD.

1103
01:02:44,962 --> 01:02:47,028
YOU WANT TO PUT IT
ON YOUR FACE?

1104
01:02:47,030 --> 01:02:50,132
OH, GOSH.
YOU HAVE SUCH A FEVER.

1105
01:02:50,134 --> 01:02:53,235
- [moaning]

1106
01:02:53,469 --> 01:02:58,039
- WE'RE GONNA GET YOU
TO A HOSPITAL.

1107
01:02:58,041 --> 01:03:02,344
ALL RIGHT, MORE WATER.

1108
01:03:02,346 --> 01:03:05,947
- [slurping]

1109
01:03:06,883 --> 01:03:07,816
- GOOD.

1110
01:03:07,818 --> 01:03:11,119
YOU'RE THIRSTY.

1111
01:03:11,121 --> 01:03:13,355
WE GOT TO KEEP YOUR FEVER DOWN,
I GUESS,

1112
01:03:13,357 --> 01:03:16,992
UNTIL WE GET TO THE HOSPITAL.

1113
01:03:16,994 --> 01:03:20,162
I LOVE YOU.

1114
01:03:22,532 --> 01:03:26,134
- [growling]

1115
01:03:28,204 --> 01:03:29,504
[yells viciously]

1116
01:03:29,506 --> 01:03:32,073
- [screaming]

1117
01:03:32,075 --> 01:03:34,976
- [growling]

1118
01:03:34,978 --> 01:03:37,045
- [muffled]
GRANDMA!

1119
01:03:37,047 --> 01:03:42,017
[screaming]

1120
01:03:43,152 --> 01:03:45,220
- OH, GOD.

1121
01:03:45,222 --> 01:03:48,356
- [snarling]

1122
01:03:48,358 --> 01:03:51,593
- [screaming]

1123
01:03:55,231 --> 01:03:56,932
[gunshot]

1124
01:03:56,934 --> 01:03:59,067
- THEY'RE EVERYWHERE, LOUIS!

1125
01:03:59,069 --> 01:04:00,402
EVERYWHERE!

1126
01:04:00,404 --> 01:04:02,537
[growling]

1127
01:04:02,539 --> 01:04:06,007
- [shrieking]

1128
01:04:06,009 --> 01:04:09,244
[driving rock music]

1129
01:04:09,246 --> 01:04:11,213
♪

1130
01:04:11,215 --> 01:04:12,981
[gunshot]

1131
01:04:16,519 --> 01:04:21,323
♪

1132
01:04:21,325 --> 01:04:23,058
[gunshot]

1133
01:04:25,328 --> 01:04:26,595
[gunshot]

1134
01:04:26,597 --> 01:04:30,332
[grunting, growling]

1135
01:04:36,239 --> 01:04:37,272
- HEY!

1136
01:04:37,274 --> 01:04:39,674
[gunshot]

1137
01:04:39,676 --> 01:04:44,279
- [snarling]

1138
01:04:48,451 --> 01:04:50,218
[gunshot]

1139
01:04:54,257 --> 01:04:56,925
♪

1140
01:04:56,927 --> 01:04:58,226
[gunshot]

1141
01:04:58,228 --> 01:05:01,196
- [screaming]

1142
01:05:01,198 --> 01:05:02,430
[gunshot]

1143
01:05:02,432 --> 01:05:03,498
- SETH!

1144
01:05:03,500 --> 01:05:07,369
- [screaming]

1145
01:05:07,371 --> 01:05:11,306
- NO!

1146
01:05:11,308 --> 01:05:15,343
- ANDREW, GET THE DOOR.

1147
01:05:15,345 --> 01:05:16,611
- [sobbing]

1148
01:05:16,613 --> 01:05:19,981
- [groaning]

1149
01:05:19,983 --> 01:05:21,416
- YOU ALL RIGHT?
- YEAH.

1150
01:05:21,418 --> 01:05:23,485
YOU OKAY?

1151
01:05:23,487 --> 01:05:25,387
- ANDREW, YOU ALL RIGHT?
- I'M OKAY.

1152
01:05:25,389 --> 01:05:27,289
- WE'RE GONNA DIE!

1153
01:05:27,291 --> 01:05:28,423
- YOU SHUT UP!

1154
01:05:28,425 --> 01:05:30,125
YOU SHUT FUCK UP!

1155
01:05:30,127 --> 01:05:32,127
IT'S NOT THE TIME
FOR THAT.

1156
01:05:32,129 --> 01:05:35,063
RIGHT NOW, WE ALL
GOT TO KEEP OUR HEADS.

1157
01:05:35,065 --> 01:05:39,000
WE HAVE TO FIGHT
AND SURVIVE!

1158
01:05:39,002 --> 01:05:40,101
WE GOT TO BUTTON
THIS PLACE UP

1159
01:05:40,103 --> 01:05:42,070
AND COVER UP
THESE DOORS AND WINDOWS.

1160
01:05:42,072 --> 01:05:44,272
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THE HELL IS OUT THERE,

1161
01:05:44,274 --> 01:05:46,174
BUT IT'S COMING BACK!

1162
01:05:46,176 --> 01:05:47,642
IT'S COMING BACK.

1163
01:05:47,644 --> 01:05:51,212
COMING BACK,
AND IT'S FUCKING HUNGRY.

1164
01:05:51,214 --> 01:05:52,647
ANDREW, GO FIND
EVERYTHING YOU CAN

1165
01:05:52,649 --> 01:05:55,550
TO PUT OVER THESE
DOORS AND WINDOWS.

1166
01:05:55,552 --> 01:05:58,420
TABLES, CHAIRS, ANYTHING.

1167
01:05:58,422 --> 01:06:00,655
MATT, YOU WITH ME?

1168
01:06:00,657 --> 01:06:02,090
- [shaky panting]

1169
01:06:02,092 --> 01:06:04,392
I'M STILL IN ONE PIECE.

1170
01:06:04,394 --> 01:06:06,661
- OKAY.
GO GET ALL THE WEAPONS.

1171
01:06:06,663 --> 01:06:09,998
ALL THE AMMO.
LOAD UP THE GUNS.

1172
01:06:10,000 --> 01:06:13,001
- [suppressed groaning]

1173
01:06:13,003 --> 01:06:17,639
OKAY.
I CAN GET IT.

1174
01:06:17,641 --> 01:06:18,573
- I'M NOT GONNA DIE.

1175
01:06:18,575 --> 01:06:23,278
I'LL KILL EVERY SINGLE ONE
OF THOSE SONS OF BITCHES.

1176
01:06:23,280 --> 01:06:28,650
DON'T ANYBODY DO ANYTHING
WITHOUT TELLING ME FIRST.

1177
01:06:32,054 --> 01:06:33,521
EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

1178
01:06:33,523 --> 01:06:37,459
- YEAH, I KNOW.
I KNOW IT WILL.

1179
01:06:37,461 --> 01:06:39,294
- [shrieking]

1180
01:06:39,296 --> 01:06:42,697
[screaming]

1181
01:06:47,770 --> 01:06:49,337
- FLIP THAT TABLE OVER.

1182
01:06:49,339 --> 01:06:53,541
PUT IT IN FRONT
OF THE WINDOW.

1183
01:07:10,793 --> 01:07:13,361
- I'M SCARED.

1184
01:07:17,566 --> 01:07:21,236
- SO AM I.

1185
01:07:21,238 --> 01:07:21,836
- I DON'T--

1186
01:07:21,838 --> 01:07:23,571
I DON'T THINK
I'M GONNA BE ABLE

1187
01:07:23,573 --> 01:07:25,673
TO KEEP UP WITH YOU GUYS.

1188
01:07:25,675 --> 01:07:27,442
I DON'T WANT TO HOLD
ANYONE BACK.

1189
01:07:27,444 --> 01:07:32,647
I JUST--
I DON'T THINK I'M GONNA MAKE IT.

1190
01:07:32,649 --> 01:07:37,118
- EVERYBODY'S
GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

1191
01:07:37,120 --> 01:07:38,186
I PROMISE.

1192
01:07:38,188 --> 01:07:42,190
EVERYONE.
ESPECIALLY YOU.

1193
01:07:42,192 --> 01:07:44,626
- WELL, WHAT ABOUT ANDREW?

1194
01:07:44,628 --> 01:07:47,562
- HE'S MY SON.

1195
01:07:50,466 --> 01:07:51,633
I'M COUNTING ON HIM.

1196
01:07:51,635 --> 01:07:54,302
- I KNOW SETH SHOWED YOU
HOW TO USE ONE OF THESE, RIGHT?

1197
01:07:54,304 --> 01:07:56,671
SLIDE THIS OPEN,
PUT THE BULLETS IN THERE,

1198
01:07:56,673 --> 01:08:00,508
CLOSE IT, AND YOU SHOOT
JUST LIKE YOUR CAMERA.

1199
01:08:00,510 --> 01:08:02,577
POINT AND SHOOT.

1200
01:08:04,480 --> 01:08:07,449
- IT FEELS LIKE
THE WORLD'S GONNA END.

1201
01:08:07,451 --> 01:08:09,184
- NO, IT'S NOT.

1202
01:08:09,186 --> 01:08:11,252
WE NEED TO GET THE FUCK
OUT OF THIS HOUSE.

1203
01:08:11,254 --> 01:08:14,589
- THEY WERE EATING SETH ALIVE
WHEN THEY DRAGGED HIM

1204
01:08:14,591 --> 01:08:16,391
OUT THE WINDOW.

1205
01:08:25,434 --> 01:08:26,201
[radio static]

1206
01:08:26,203 --> 01:08:28,436
- A GREAT DEAL IS UNKNOWN
ABOUT LYME DISEASE.

1207
01:08:28,438 --> 01:08:30,805
IN MOST CASES, LYME DISEASE,
WHEN TREATED EARLY,

1208
01:08:30,807 --> 01:08:34,142
IS A MILD ILLNESS
WITH NO LONG-TERM EFFECT.

1209
01:08:34,144 --> 01:08:36,544
THERE NOW SEEMS TO BE
A NEW STRAIN,

1210
01:08:36,546 --> 01:08:38,379
A STRAIN OF LYME
THAT IS ACTUALLY

1211
01:08:38,381 --> 01:08:39,848
A COMBINATION OF STRAINS.

1212
01:08:39,850 --> 01:08:42,183
HOWEVER, THIS NEW,
EVOLVED STRAIN

1213
01:08:42,185 --> 01:08:43,151
IS FAR MORE AGGRESSIVE.

1214
01:08:43,153 --> 01:08:46,654
IT IS CAUSING VIOLENT,
ANIMALISTIC BEHAVIOR--

1215
01:08:46,656 --> 01:08:48,189
DOG-LIKE BITING ATTACKS.

1216
01:08:48,191 --> 01:08:51,793
THE SPREAD RATE AND DEATH TOLL
IS RISING TO DISTURBING NUMBERS.

1217
01:08:51,795 --> 01:08:55,430
SYMPTOMS CAN BE FLU-LIKE:
HIGH FEVER, FATIGUE.

1218
01:08:55,432 --> 01:08:57,432
OTHER SYMPTOMS
MAY BE QUITE SEVERE:

1219
01:08:57,434 --> 01:09:00,735
DELUSIONS, HALLUCINATIONS
CAUSING SOME TO BE BEDRIDDEN

1220
01:09:00,737 --> 01:09:04,472
IN A NON-RESPONSIVE,
OPEN-EYED, COMA-LIKE STATE.

1221
01:09:04,474 --> 01:09:08,176
THE MEDICAL RELIEF STATIONS
ARE FILLING UP FAST.

1222
01:09:08,178 --> 01:09:11,246
I REGRET TO BE THE MESSENGER
FOR SUCH BAD NEWS,

1223
01:09:11,248 --> 01:09:14,282
AND TO ALL WHO
CAN HEAR MY VOICE,

1224
01:09:14,284 --> 01:09:17,185
BE CAREFUL.

1225
01:09:17,187 --> 01:09:19,454
- OKAY.

1226
01:09:19,456 --> 01:09:21,623
EVERYBODY HEARD THAT.

1227
01:09:21,625 --> 01:09:23,791
I THINK IT'S OUR BEST SHOT.

1228
01:09:23,793 --> 01:09:25,627
GET TO ONE OF THOSE
RELIEF STATIONS.

1229
01:09:25,629 --> 01:09:28,596
- THE CLOSEST ONE'S
25 MILES AWAY.

1230
01:09:28,598 --> 01:09:34,302
- HOW WE GONNA GO THAT FAR
WITH ALL THOSE THINGS OUT THERE?

1231
01:09:34,304 --> 01:09:37,705
- DO THE BEST WE CAN.

1232
01:09:37,707 --> 01:09:40,909
WE'RE PROBABLY
BETTER OFF THAN MOST.

1233
01:09:40,911 --> 01:09:43,578
WE GOT A LOT
OF PROVISIONS.

1234
01:09:43,580 --> 01:09:45,280
PLENTY OF AMMO.

1235
01:09:45,282 --> 01:09:47,982
- ALL RIGHT, WHY DON'T WE TAKE
DR. DENNEHEY'S TRUCK?

1236
01:09:47,984 --> 01:09:52,720
THING'S LIKE A FUCKING TANK.

1237
01:09:52,722 --> 01:09:55,823
- IT'S A GOOD IDEA.

1238
01:09:55,825 --> 01:09:57,292
[squishing]

1239
01:09:57,294 --> 01:09:58,893
MATT.

1240
01:09:58,895 --> 01:10:01,396
QUIT FOOLING AROUND
WITH THAT MEAT.

1241
01:10:01,398 --> 01:10:04,933
I'M TELLING YOU,
PUT IT AWAY.

1242
01:10:07,903 --> 01:10:10,838
- OKAY, PAL.

1243
01:10:17,713 --> 01:10:20,615
- LISTEN,
EVERYBODY'S PRETTY TIRED.

1244
01:10:20,617 --> 01:10:21,983
I DON'T THINK
IT'S A GREAT IDEA

1245
01:10:21,985 --> 01:10:25,286
TO GO WANDERING
OUT IN THE DARKNESS.

1246
01:10:25,288 --> 01:10:28,790
LOOK, WE MIGHT
BE ALL RIGHT FOR THE NIGHT.

1247
01:10:28,792 --> 01:10:33,328
I SAY WE SET OUT
FIRST THING IN THE MORNING.

1248
01:10:45,674 --> 01:10:49,310
[clattering from above]

1249
01:10:49,312 --> 01:10:50,445
YOU HEAR THAT?

1250
01:10:50,447 --> 01:10:54,382
GO UPSTAIRS AND MAKE SURE HE HAS
THE BEDROOMS ALL BUTTONED UP.

1251
01:10:54,384 --> 01:10:57,285
BE CAREFUL.

1252
01:11:00,055 --> 01:11:02,557
[gun cocking]

1253
01:11:02,559 --> 01:11:05,627
[ominous music]

1254
01:11:05,629 --> 01:11:13,935
♪

1255
01:11:17,539 --> 01:11:21,075
[clattering from above]

1256
01:11:25,014 --> 01:11:26,447
- ANDREW,
WHAT HAPPENED?

1257
01:11:26,449 --> 01:11:28,583
- THERE'S NOTHING UP THERE.
I CHECKED EVERY DOOR.

1258
01:11:28,585 --> 01:11:30,885
- I'M HEARING ALL KINDS
OF SHIT OUTSIDE, MAN.

1259
01:11:30,887 --> 01:11:32,854
THEY'RE EVERYWHERE.

1260
01:11:32,856 --> 01:11:34,355
GO WATCH THE DOOR.

1261
01:11:34,357 --> 01:11:36,658
I DON'T FEEL FUCKING GOOD, MAN.

1262
01:11:36,660 --> 01:11:39,527
HOLY SHIT.

1263
01:11:39,529 --> 01:11:43,097
- [panting fearfully]

1264
01:11:43,832 --> 01:11:44,932
LOUIS!
- SETH!

1265
01:11:44,934 --> 01:11:46,701
- PLEASE LET ME IN!
IT'S SETH!

1266
01:11:46,703 --> 01:11:48,469
- PLEASE!
- NO, NO, NO!

1267
01:11:48,471 --> 01:11:49,404
DON'T OPEN THE DOOR.

1268
01:11:49,406 --> 01:11:51,906
NOBODY'S COMING IN HERE.
I DON'T CARE WHO IT IS.

1269
01:11:51,908 --> 01:11:52,874
NO ONE'S COMING IN.

1270
01:11:52,876 --> 01:11:56,811
- IT'S SETH!
PLEASE LET ME IN!

1271
01:11:56,813 --> 01:11:58,012
JESSICA!

1272
01:11:58,014 --> 01:12:00,448
JESSICA, JESSICA,
PLEASE HELP ME!

1273
01:12:00,450 --> 01:12:01,916
DON'T LET THE FUCKING--
- WE HAVE TO HELP HIM.

1274
01:12:01,918 --> 01:12:04,018
- HE'S NOT COMING IN.
SETH, GET THE FUCK OUT OF HERE!

1275
01:12:04,020 --> 01:12:06,888
- PLEASE LET ME IN, PLEASE!
- YOU'RE NOT COMING IN.

1276
01:12:06,890 --> 01:12:07,755
- PLEASE LET ME IN.

1277
01:12:07,757 --> 01:12:13,061
DON'T FUCKING LET THEM
GET ME, LOUIS!

1278
01:12:13,063 --> 01:12:13,861
JESSICA!

1279
01:12:13,863 --> 01:12:17,799
JESSICA, PLEASE,
OPEN THE FUCKING DOOR.

1280
01:12:17,801 --> 01:12:18,766
PLEASE!

1281
01:12:18,768 --> 01:12:20,435
[snarling]

1282
01:12:20,437 --> 01:12:23,971
- NO, NO, NO!
- OH, GOD.

1283
01:12:23,973 --> 01:12:27,842
[snarling, grunting]

1284
01:12:27,844 --> 01:12:32,580
- [growling]
- [screams]

1285
01:12:32,582 --> 01:12:34,148
- GET THE FUCK OFF HIM.

1286
01:12:34,150 --> 01:12:37,118
[gunshot]

1287
01:12:37,120 --> 01:12:39,120
[screaming]

1288
01:12:39,122 --> 01:12:41,756
- OH, FUCK.
- LAY DOWN.

1289
01:12:41,758 --> 01:12:42,724
ANGELA, LAY DOWN.

1290
01:12:42,726 --> 01:12:44,525
- AH, MY WATER BROKE.

1291
01:12:44,527 --> 01:12:46,694
- LAY DOWN, LAY DOWN.
NOT NOW.

1292
01:12:46,696 --> 01:12:48,129
CAN'T DO THIS NOW,
NOT HERE.

1293
01:12:48,131 --> 01:12:50,998
LISTEN, I TOLD YOU
ONE OF THOSE FUCKING THINGS

1294
01:12:51,000 --> 01:12:52,734
BIT ME IN THE ARM.

1295
01:12:52,736 --> 01:12:55,603
I THINK I HAVE--
I DON'T KNOW.

1296
01:12:55,605 --> 01:12:57,405
WE GOT A GAME CHANGE.

1297
01:12:57,407 --> 01:12:58,740
EVERYTHING'S CHANGED.

1298
01:12:58,742 --> 01:13:00,775
THEY'RE OUTSIDE.
THEY'RE COMING BACK IN.

1299
01:13:00,777 --> 01:13:02,510
YOU GOT TO GET
TO A MEDICAL CENTER.

1300
01:13:02,512 --> 01:13:03,478
- NO.
NO, PLEASE.

1301
01:13:03,480 --> 01:13:04,846
- GOT TO GET HER OUT OF HERE.
- NO, NO.

1302
01:13:04,848 --> 01:13:06,180
- WE GOT TO GO.
I'M GETTING ED'S TRUCK.

1303
01:13:06,182 --> 01:13:08,616
- NO, DON'T GO OUT THERE.
DON'T GO OUT THERE.

1304
01:13:08,618 --> 01:13:09,984
- I HAVE TO GO.
JUST LAY BACK.

1305
01:13:09,986 --> 01:13:11,452
LAY BACK, LAY BACK.

1306
01:13:11,454 --> 01:13:12,787
- I GOT YOU.
I GOT YOU.

1307
01:13:12,789 --> 01:13:16,190
- [groaning]

1308
01:13:17,192 --> 01:13:19,127
- LET'S GO!

1309
01:13:19,129 --> 01:13:20,695
- STOP.
I'LL GET THE TRUCK.

1310
01:13:20,697 --> 01:13:23,564
EVEN IF THE KEYS AREN'T IN IT,
I'LL GET IT RUNNING.

1311
01:13:23,566 --> 01:13:26,100
I'M A LOT FASTER
THAN YOU.

1312
01:13:29,905 --> 01:13:31,939
- [chuckling]

1313
01:13:31,941 --> 01:13:34,642
GIVE ME A CIGARETTE.

1314
01:13:34,644 --> 01:13:38,646
- ALL RIGHT.

1315
01:13:40,015 --> 01:13:43,184
YOU DON'T LOOK
TOO GOOD.

1316
01:13:44,953 --> 01:13:51,192
- YEAH, WELL, ONE OF THOSE
FUCKING THINGS BIT ME.

1317
01:13:52,761 --> 01:13:54,962
I DON'T WANT TO GET IT.

1318
01:13:54,964 --> 01:13:59,734
I DON'T WANT TO GET IT, ANDREW.
IF I GOT IT...

1319
01:14:00,903 --> 01:14:04,939
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU GOT TO DO.

1320
01:14:04,941 --> 01:14:06,007
YOU GOT TO PUT ME AWAY.

1321
01:14:06,009 --> 01:14:08,943
- I'M NOT FUCKING DOING THAT.

1322
01:14:08,945 --> 01:14:10,044
YOU CRAZY?

1323
01:14:10,046 --> 01:14:11,979
I'M GONNA GET THE TRUCK,
WE'RE GONNA PUT THE GIRLS

1324
01:14:11,981 --> 01:14:16,684
IN THE TRUCK, WE'RE GONNA GET
THE FUCK OUT OF HERE.

1325
01:14:20,556 --> 01:14:23,791
I GOT TO DO THIS.

1326
01:14:29,932 --> 01:14:31,933
- BE CAREFUL, ANDREW.

1327
01:14:31,935 --> 01:14:33,968
PLEASE BE CAREFUL.

1328
01:14:33,970 --> 01:14:37,171
LET'S GET THIS SHIT
OFF THE DOOR.

1329
01:14:41,877 --> 01:14:45,112
[ominous warbling music]

1330
01:14:45,114 --> 01:14:48,783
♪

1331
01:14:48,785 --> 01:14:52,186
- [snarling]

1332
01:15:19,648 --> 01:15:20,648
- [growling]

1333
01:15:20,650 --> 01:15:24,118
[intense rock music]

1334
01:15:24,120 --> 01:15:25,152
- FUCK, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

1335
01:15:25,154 --> 01:15:28,623
- [snarling]
- DON'T DO THAT!

1336
01:15:28,625 --> 01:15:31,726
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING, SETH?

1337
01:15:31,728 --> 01:15:40,034
♪

1338
01:15:40,869 --> 01:15:44,272
- [grunting]

1339
01:15:51,613 --> 01:15:52,980
- STOP, SETH!

1340
01:15:52,982 --> 01:15:53,614
STOP!

1341
01:15:53,616 --> 01:15:56,851
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING?

1342
01:15:58,253 --> 01:16:02,056
- COME AND GET IT!

1343
01:16:02,058 --> 01:16:04,325
[blade zipping]

1344
01:16:34,056 --> 01:16:36,357
- YOU ALL RIGHT?

1345
01:16:37,192 --> 01:16:39,727
WHAT HAPPENED?
WHAT'S ALL THAT BLOOD FROM?

1346
01:16:39,729 --> 01:16:40,995
- IT'S NOT MINE.

1347
01:16:40,997 --> 01:16:42,396
I SAW SETH.

1348
01:16:42,398 --> 01:16:43,965
HE TRIED TO KILL ME.

1349
01:16:43,967 --> 01:16:45,733
DOCTOR ED KILLED HIM,

1350
01:16:45,735 --> 01:16:47,034
BUT HE'S GONE NOW.

1351
01:16:47,036 --> 01:16:49,370
THEY'RE FUCKING MONSTERS.

1352
01:16:49,372 --> 01:16:50,404
THEIR FLESH IS ALL FUCKED UP.

1353
01:16:50,406 --> 01:16:53,741
I DON'T KNOW WHAT THE FUCK'S
GOING ON, DAD.

1354
01:16:53,743 --> 01:16:55,042
- COME ON!
LET'S GO!

1355
01:16:55,044 --> 01:16:57,845
GET YOUR STUFF.
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

1356
01:16:57,847 --> 01:17:00,047
RIGHT NOW.

1357
01:17:00,049 --> 01:17:03,718
COME ON.
COME ON, LET'S GO.

1358
01:17:03,720 --> 01:17:04,318
- [moans]

1359
01:17:04,320 --> 01:17:06,220
- WHERE THE FUCK IS JESSICA?

1360
01:17:06,222 --> 01:17:07,688
WHERE'S MATT?

1361
01:17:07,690 --> 01:17:08,923
- [screams]

1362
01:17:08,925 --> 01:17:10,057
MATTHEW!

1363
01:17:10,059 --> 01:17:11,993
[shrieks]

1364
01:17:16,198 --> 01:17:18,933
- MATT, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

1365
01:17:18,935 --> 01:17:21,869
MATT--
GET HIM OFF ME.

1366
01:17:21,871 --> 01:17:24,238
[clanging]

1367
01:17:24,240 --> 01:17:26,807
GET HIM OFF OF ME!

1368
01:17:30,345 --> 01:17:32,279
[gunshot]

1369
01:17:40,022 --> 01:17:42,456
LET'S GO.

1370
01:17:42,458 --> 01:17:45,826
ANDREW, PUT THEM IN THE CAR.

1371
01:17:45,828 --> 01:17:47,328
[gunshot]
- COME ON, GET IN.

1372
01:17:47,330 --> 01:17:49,196
[gunshot]
LET'S GO, DAD!

1373
01:17:49,198 --> 01:17:50,331
- GET IN!

1374
01:17:50,333 --> 01:17:51,999
[gunshot]

1375
01:17:52,001 --> 01:17:54,335
[gunshot]

1376
01:17:54,337 --> 01:17:56,103
[gunshot]

1377
01:17:59,808 --> 01:18:03,210
[gunshot, shrieking]

1378
01:18:03,779 --> 01:18:06,113
LET'S GO, LET'S GO, LET'S GO!

1379
01:18:06,115 --> 01:18:08,749
[gunshot]

1380
01:18:08,751 --> 01:18:10,317
- [snarls]

1381
01:18:12,788 --> 01:18:15,456
- [bellowing]

1382
01:18:32,908 --> 01:18:36,777
[all grunting and snarling]

1383
01:18:52,260 --> 01:18:54,495
- ED.

1384
01:18:58,066 --> 01:19:02,036
- YOU'RE INFECTED, LOUIS.

1385
01:19:02,038 --> 01:19:03,237
- I KNOW.

1386
01:19:03,239 --> 01:19:05,940
- LOCK YOURSELF UP.

1387
01:19:05,942 --> 01:19:10,044
CHAIN YOURSELF
IF YOU HAVE TO.

1388
01:19:10,046 --> 01:19:12,346
IT'S A VIRUS.

1389
01:19:12,348 --> 01:19:17,351
IF YOU CAN CONTROL THE FEVER,
YOU CAN MAINTAIN,

1390
01:19:17,353 --> 01:19:21,489
BUT WHATEVER YOU DO,
DO NOT GIVE IN

1391
01:19:21,491 --> 01:19:28,329
TO THE MADDENING COMPULSION
TO EAT HUMAN FLESH.

1392
01:19:28,331 --> 01:19:32,166
[all moaning and growling]

1393
01:19:35,036 --> 01:19:38,305
- ED, LET'S GO.

1394
01:19:43,879 --> 01:19:47,114
- IT'S TOO LATE FOR ME.

1395
01:19:47,116 --> 01:19:48,983
- [howls]

1396
01:19:48,985 --> 01:19:50,184
- ED!

1397
01:19:50,186 --> 01:19:51,519
ED!
- COME ON, DAD!

1398
01:19:51,521 --> 01:19:53,320
- [sobbing]
ED!

1399
01:19:53,322 --> 01:19:57,291
[all moaning and snarling]

1400
01:20:02,063 --> 01:20:04,064
YOU MOTHERFUCKERS!

1401
01:20:04,066 --> 01:20:05,966
[gunshot]

1402
01:20:08,470 --> 01:20:11,972
[eerie ambient music]

1403
01:20:11,974 --> 01:20:20,281
♪

1404
01:20:36,565 --> 01:20:41,902
WE DIDN'T MAKE IT TO
THE MEDICAL STATION THAT NIGHT.

1405
01:20:41,904 --> 01:20:45,005
THERE WAS TOO MANY OF THEM.

1406
01:20:45,007 --> 01:20:47,374
WE GOT OVERWHELMED.

1407
01:20:47,376 --> 01:20:51,912
THE INFECTED, THEY GATHERED,
THEY ROSE, AND THEY ATTACKED

1408
01:20:51,914 --> 01:20:53,914
AGAIN AND AGAIN,

1409
01:20:53,916 --> 01:20:55,449
FURTHER SPREADING THE VIRUS,

1410
01:20:55,451 --> 01:20:59,086
LEAVING NOTHING
BUT MORE LOST SOULS,

1411
01:20:59,088 --> 01:21:01,622
CARNAGE IN THEIR WAKE.

1412
01:21:06,528 --> 01:21:14,034
IT'S HARD TO REMEMBER,
TO MAKE SENSE OF IT ALL NOW

1413
01:21:14,036 --> 01:21:16,971
AND HOW IT ALL HAPPENED.

1414
01:21:33,021 --> 01:21:36,991
I LOST ANGELA AND THE BABY.

1415
01:21:36,993 --> 01:21:40,628
[sobbing]

1416
01:21:40,630 --> 01:21:44,198
[groaning]

1417
01:21:50,171 --> 01:21:52,940
I THOUGHT I HAD LOST
ALL HOPE FOR MYSELF

1418
01:21:52,942 --> 01:21:56,977
ALONG WITH THEM...

1419
01:22:04,386 --> 01:22:08,756
BUT I CAN'T QUIT
ON MY SON.

1420
01:22:08,758 --> 01:22:11,425
I CAN'T QUIT
ON ANDREW.

1421
01:22:11,427 --> 01:22:14,361
I DIDN'T GIVE HIM
WHAT A BOY NEEDS FROM A FATHER

1422
01:22:14,363 --> 01:22:18,132
TO BECOME A MAN AND SURVIVE
IN THE CIVILIZED WORLD,

1423
01:22:18,134 --> 01:22:20,601
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT
TO CALL IT.

1424
01:22:20,603 --> 01:22:23,203
I NEED TO HOLD ON TO THIS
LONG ENOUGH TO MAKE SURE

1425
01:22:23,205 --> 01:22:26,073
HE'S GOT A SHOT
AT WHATEVER'S LEFT

1426
01:22:26,075 --> 01:22:27,975
OF WHAT WE HAVE.

1427
01:22:27,977 --> 01:22:29,543
THAT'S HIS WORLD NOW,

1428
01:22:29,545 --> 01:22:32,079
THE WORLD WHERE THE VIRUS
AND THE PLAGUE

1429
01:22:32,081 --> 01:22:35,015
HAS BROKEN DOWN SOCIETY.

1430
01:23:04,379 --> 01:23:07,414
BEFORE WE CAN REBUILD,
WE HAVE TO FIND A WAY

1431
01:23:07,416 --> 01:23:11,485
TO SURVIVE OURSELVES...

1432
01:23:11,487 --> 01:23:14,121
A WAY TO FIGHT.

1433
01:23:41,282 --> 01:23:43,450
WE BUILT A VEHICLE.

1434
01:23:43,452 --> 01:23:47,421
WE CALL IT
THE WAR WAGON.

1435
01:23:49,391 --> 01:23:52,593
[pulsing rock music]

1436
01:23:52,595 --> 01:23:55,262
♪

1437
01:23:55,264 --> 01:23:57,398
[engine revving]

1438
01:23:57,400 --> 01:24:00,601
[dark rock music]

1439
01:24:00,603 --> 01:24:09,109
♪

1440
01:24:22,357 --> 01:24:28,095
EVERY DAY, WE VENTURE OUT
FURTHER AND FURTHER

1441
01:24:28,097 --> 01:24:32,599
TRYING TO GET
MEDICAL SUPPLIES.

1442
01:24:32,601 --> 01:24:35,836
GET FOOD, WATER.

1443
01:24:37,439 --> 01:24:43,143
ANYTHING WE CAN FIND
THAT'S STILL OUT THERE.

1444
01:25:46,241 --> 01:25:49,476
[suspenseful music]

1445
01:25:49,478 --> 01:25:57,784
♪

1446
01:26:55,543 --> 01:26:57,377
[clanging]

1447
01:26:58,913 --> 01:27:02,349
[suspenseful music]

1448
01:27:02,351 --> 01:27:10,691
♪

1449
01:28:00,608 --> 01:28:03,477
THERE SEEMS TO BE
NO HELP,

1450
01:28:03,479 --> 01:28:06,747
NO GOVERNMENT INTERVENTION.

1451
01:28:07,615 --> 01:28:10,951
IT'S ONLY WHAT WE KNOW.

1452
01:28:17,125 --> 01:28:22,429
THIS THING HAS SPREAD
ALL OVER THE WORLD,

1453
01:28:22,431 --> 01:28:24,498
AS FAR AS THE EYE CAN SEE,

1454
01:28:24,500 --> 01:28:28,802
AS FAR AS THE RADIO
AND TELEVISION CAN TELL.

1455
01:28:58,900 --> 01:29:01,101
[rooster crowing]

1456
01:29:01,103 --> 01:29:04,104
THERE IS ALWAYS HOPE,

1457
01:29:04,106 --> 01:29:08,909
A SAFE HAVEN,

1458
01:29:08,911 --> 01:29:11,845
A FORT OF PROTECTION.

1459
01:29:11,847 --> 01:29:14,915
- ALL RIGHT.

1460
01:29:14,917 --> 01:29:17,784
- THAT'S ALL WE HAVE.

1461
01:29:18,720 --> 01:29:21,988
[wistful rock music]

1462
01:29:21,990 --> 01:29:30,464
♪

1463
01:29:31,699 --> 01:29:34,701
[speaking indistinctly]

1464
01:29:49,450 --> 01:29:50,951
- HELLO.

1465
01:29:52,687 --> 01:29:56,123
- EVERY DAY,
WE HOPE THAT IT'S OVER,

1466
01:29:56,125 --> 01:30:01,495
AND EACH NIGHT,
OUR NIGHTMARES REMIND US

1467
01:30:01,497 --> 01:30:04,598
THAT IT'S NOT.

1468
01:30:21,783 --> 01:30:27,087
MAYBE SOMEDAY WE'LL FIND
AN END TO ALL OF THIS.

1469
01:30:27,089 --> 01:30:31,858
UNTIL THEN,
WE KEEP FIGHTING.

1470
01:30:31,860 --> 01:30:35,195
GOD HELP US.
AMEN.

1471
01:31:08,229 --> 01:31:12,032
- [groaning]

1472
01:31:12,034 --> 01:31:14,134
WHO'S THERE?

1473
01:31:14,136 --> 01:31:17,871
[grunting furiously]

1474
01:31:19,974 --> 01:31:23,543
[yelling]

1475
01:31:36,591 --> 01:31:39,960
[screaming]

1476
01:31:51,005 --> 01:31:54,574
[moaning]

1477
01:32:11,359 --> 01:32:13,960
- YOU KNOW,
A LOT OF STRANGE THINGS

1478
01:32:13,962 --> 01:32:16,296
HAPPEN OUT IN THE WOODS.

1479
01:32:22,803 --> 01:32:24,871
- IT'S A VIRUS.

1480
01:32:34,649 --> 01:32:37,918
- WILD
AND ANIMALISTIC BEHAVIOR.

1481
01:32:37,920 --> 01:32:40,086
HIGH FEVER AND FATIGUE.

1482
01:32:48,129 --> 01:32:51,031
DOG-LIKE BITING ATTACKS.

1483
01:33:14,121 --> 01:33:18,858
- IF YOU CAN CONTROL THE FEVER,
YOU CAN MAINTAIN.

1484
01:33:30,004 --> 01:33:32,372
- DO DEER EAT MEAT?

1485
01:33:48,956 --> 01:33:52,058
- I'LL DO ANYTHING YOU WANT.

1486
01:33:52,060 --> 01:33:54,094
ANYTHING.

